12.007 - TRAINERS 12.007.01 Each trainer must obtain a license from the Racing Commission.
The trainer shall list on the application for said license all the names of owners or part owners of all horses trained unless this requirement is waived or modified by the Commission.
12.007.02 No trainer shall harbor on the grounds of an association, engage or employ any unlicensed person.
The Commission may require each trainer to register in their office every person employed by that trainer.
12.007.03 No trainer of race horses shall register under a stable name nor shall practice said profession except under his or her own legal name.
(See Statute 2-1220.)
