16.002 PRODUCE RACES 16.002.01 In naming an entry for a produce race, the produce is entered by specifying the dam and sire or sires.
16.002.02 If a mare entered in a produce race drops her foal before January 1st, or if she has a dead, or more than one foal, or is barren, the entry of such mare is void.
