16.002.05 Failure to register a foal shall not exempt the nominator from any liability he may incur under the Rules.
16.002.06 The nominator in produce races, or races in which nominations of foals are made, shall be released from further liability with regard to the entry by filing an acceptable transfer of entry prior to the declaration date stated in the conditions of the race.
